ion shows a 7:75x and\n12x reduction in prediction error compared to the Halide and TVM models,\nrespectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Aug 2021 20:20:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-31"}
