d misuses. Interestingly, our results suggest that\nexisting distance algorithms are not reliable for comparing API usage graphs.\nTo improve on this situation, we identified and discuss the algorithms' issues,\nbased on which we formulate hypotheses to initiate research on overcoming them.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Aug 2021 21:43:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-31"}
