e extreme youth of M17 MIR\nsuggests that minor accretion bursts are frequent in the earliest stages of\nmassive star formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 28 Aug 2021 02:35:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Oct 2021 07:46:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-30"}
