perform a common LO (CLO), and the additive\ntransmit distortion degrades more the performance than the additive receive\ndistortion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 28 Aug 2021 13:03:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-31"}
